author: Al Jazeera
title: California suffered state's deadliest day of coronavirus outbreak
description: The US state recorded 115 new deaths from COVID-19 over the past 24 hours.
content:
California recorded 115 deaths from COVID-19 over the past 24 hours, the state's deadliest day of the coronavirus pandemic, Governor Gavin Newsom said on Thursday.
